  <summary>1/6/1999--Introduced.
Prohibits the manufacture, sale, delivery, or importation of any bus (including a school bus) designed to transport more than 15 passengers, including the driver, that is not equipped with seat belts. Sets forth civil penalties for violation of this prohibition.</summary>
